&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Head of PMO &lt;/strong&gt;is responsible for driving delivery excellence across the Professional Services organization by establishing and enforcing best-in-class project management standards, governance, and execution practices within a fintech environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
