&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market Data Analysis and Onboarding:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Analyze market data based on requirements from customers, Product Management, and other stakeholders, interact with market data vendors to ensure the data meets our standards for coverage and quality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Develop Jupyter notebooks to prototype data onboarding processes, including loading data from vendor APIs or databases, field mapping, and data transformation for storage in Snowflake.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Define and implement data validation to maintain data integrity during onboarding.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Leverage AI-enabled tools where appropriate to streamline data analysis, identify anomalies, summarize complex datasets, and improve the efficiency of market data onboarding and validation workflows.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
