&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Maintain portfolio-level reporting on project status, budget, risks, issues, and delivery forecasts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quo

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Since our founding in 1996, we have been at the vanguard of financial technology, providing groundbreaking expertise, quantitative analytics and software that redefine pricing and risk management in the financial markets. With the strategic acquisitions of FINCAD, PolyPaths and Kynex, Numerix has further strengthened its leadership position empowering financial institutions worldwide, to transform risk into opportunities with confidence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are seeking a driven Sales Executive with 2–4 years of SDR experience who is ready to progress from setting meetings to running deals. In this hybrid role, you will own the full sales cycle for smaller opportunities while sharpening the skills — discovery, deal strategy, stakeholder management, and close planning — that define elite enterprise sellers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our sales motion is powered by Claude AI across account targeting, pre-call planning, and post-call coaching. Candidates already fluent with Claude or comparable AI tools will hit the ground running and have a clear advantage from day one.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Stepping Stone to Full Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This role is purpose-built for experienced SDRs who are ready to take the next step toward a full-cycle closing role. You will own the complete sales motion for deals up to $50,000 ARR — from first outreach through signed contract — while continuing to prospect and qualify larger opportunities that you will hand off to our Senior Account Executives. It is the ideal bridge between top-of-funnel mastery and full-stack enterprise selling.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How We Use Claude AI on This Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our sales motion is built around Claude. We use it to identify and prioritize target accounts based on market signals, build deep pre-call research and talk-track briefs, analyze call recordings for coaching and deal inspection, and sharpen outbound messaging. Sales Executives who join with hands-on Claude experience — whether from prior roles, personal projects, or genuine curiosity — will contribute meaningfully from day one.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
